description:
The Brawler has certainly paid her dues. She has wrestled The Nightmare, The Goddess and Vendetta. Now that she’s had the mat time with experienced wrestlers, she can show off to us what she has learned.

The Deceptacon so names herself because she states that people underestimate her all the time. She is VERY strong and likes to rough it up. However on Ultimatesurrender, experience has the track record for victories over strength and determination.
title: The Brawler (0-3) The Deceptacon (0-0)
